snippet.title: Saleblazers Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1419850/Saleblazers/
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/W2T3qnsEQF

Saleblazers is a multiplayer shopkeeping survival game set on a perilous island environment. Build the best shopping district of all time solo, or with friends!
